text:
Natalya Alexandrova (born 27 May 1987) is a female water polo player of Kazakhstan.
She was part of the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team at the 2011 World Aquatics Championships, the 2012 Women's Olympic Qualification Tournament, and 2014 FINA Women's Water Polo World League.
